videos.headline: Watson's catch puts Northwestern State in the lead
videos.description: J.D. Almond connects with Jaylen Watson through two defenders for a 52-yard touchdown.

videos.headline: NSU fumbles on return and  scoops it up for a LA Tech TD
videos.description: Zaxier Bell fumbles on the return at their own 23-yard line, DeJuawn Oliver picks it up and runs it in for a touchdown.

videos.headline: Morgan's TD ties the game
videos.description: Bobby Chan-Chan completes a pass to Lucas Morgan for a 27-yard touchdown to tie the game.

videos.headline: Bonnette extends the lead with a 36-yard TD
videos.description: J'Mar Smith connects with Rhashid Bonnette in the end zone for a 36-yard touchdown to extend the Bulldogs lead.
